The paper proposes a method for learning embeddings of entities and relations in knowledge graphs, which is a common task in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The method is designed to efficiently handle large datasets, which is a common concern in database systems (cs.DB). The paper also evaluates the proposed method on link prediction tasks, which is a common task in natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
